BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 754.00 Tm (department has employees, but the employees existed before they joined, and if the department is) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 738.80 Tm (shut down tomorrow, the employees do not vanish - they just move to another department. The) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 723.60 Tm (department groups them, but does not own their existence.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 703.40 Tm (So here is the one simple question that tells you which is which - and I want you to actually use) Tj ET
