BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 389.00 Tm (employees are in each department. Reading, sorting, grouping - all the things we learned.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 368.80 Tm (Act three - write. Finally, we open a PrintWriter and write the processed results back out to a brand) Tj ET
