BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 333.40 Tm (Step back and look at what just happened. In one short program, we used the ArrayList, sorting,) Tj ET
BT /F1 11.00 Tf 0.120 0.120 0.140 rg 1 0 0 1 72.00 318.20 Tm (Comparator, HashMap, the BufferedReader, the BufferedWriter, and the PrintWriter. Every single) Tj ET
